>>NOORY: Douglas Dietrich on
"Beyond Belief," a little bit

00:48:22.246 --> 00:48:24.230 align:middle line:10%
of history-- many
things that we just

00:48:24.230 --> 00:48:27.380 align:middle line:10%
didn't hear about
a long time ago.

